ection techniques </span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Phishing detection techniques </span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Cloud security services &nbsp;</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '2021-09-14 07:57:19');

